617","tid":2167162,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:56:22.000Z","msg":"行好運有咩例子"},{"pid":"cab8825726c2980c57c8624beb5c6681bf1662f7","tid":2167162,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94a6b7daf53102460a6ee68080638a82aba00617","tid":2167162,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:56:22.000Z","msg":"行好運有咩例子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:59:54.000Z","msg":"你想要乜例子？<br />\n<br />\n行運都有分財官印食比，唔同方面，好少 5 樣都好，不過多數人都係睇財、官就夠<br />\n<br />\n財運好咪業績 / 個人 performance / 投資好（主要做生意 / 銷售先有利）<br />\n<br />\n官運好就易升職加人工<br />\n<br />\n男人財運好咪「囡」運都好<br />\n<br />\n女人官運好咪「仔」運都好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42921e339d31a6d6036fa53603813b75407fc37d","tid":2167162,"uid":71726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:18:47.000Z","msg":"男命身弱忌財忌官都幾蝕抵"},{"pid":"c705d524c30cd90a96e2dd57d9e04241fb6112d4","tid":2167162,"uid":187216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:50:45.000Z","msg":"IT狗幾時再交流吓？"},{"pid":"03dcb1ea99d2732344abb3b33fc33f3a8a4bc2d3","tid":2167162,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:55:25.000Z","msg":"你係咪倒轉。。。20年好運  80年1般／衰運？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d4f621647231c530a9ed339318d8eed66bd974","tid":2167162,"uid":58503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:01:25.000Z","msg":"對於好運，衰運，我會覺得好睇你心態夠唔夠樂觀知足。最簡單嘅例子，過完試工期，老細加10％人工，知足嘅人會覺得係件好事，因為有人工加。唔知足嘅人會覺得係件壞事，因為加人工加得少。"},{"pid":"19042afcfb705251a70bee28e2e0633936cd2170","tid":2167162,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c705d524c30cd90a96e2dd57d9e04241fb6112d4","tid":2167162,"uid":187216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:50:45.000Z","msg":"IT狗幾時再交流吓？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:42:24.000Z","msg":"交流啲咩？仲未熟晒斷氣同拆合<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0311ae0f82687a3841aa8a4c15fda6b15a6bf9d3","tid":2167162,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99d4f621647231c530a9ed339318d8eed66bd974","tid":2167162,"uid":58503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:01:25.000Z","msg":"對於好運，衰運，我會覺得好睇你心態夠唔夠樂觀知足。最簡單嘅例子，過完試工期，老細加10％人工，知足嘅人會覺得係件好事，因為有人工加。唔知足嘅人會覺得係件壞事，因為加人工加得少。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:47:55.000Z","msg":"啱，所以八字都係同自己比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲人本命日主受剋，你話佢哋係咪好差，又未必<br />\n<br />\n如果佢把握到日主缺困嘅流年流月嘅運勢，佢哋會好好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有事情都係相對嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077d254334b7990b30d06f767185245e058c6b25","tid":2167162,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c705d524c30cd90a96e2dd57d9e04241fb6112d4","tid":2167162,"uid":187216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:50:45.000Z","msg":"IT狗幾時再交流吓？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd390a58a61110d77982b8602248d019a6b72a5","tid":2167162,"uid":41050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"077d254334b7990b30d06f767185245e058c6b25","tid":2167162,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c705d524c30cd90a96e2dd57d9e04241fb6112d4","tid":2167162,"uid":187216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:50:45.000Z","msg":"IT狗幾時再交流吓？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:50:29.000Z","msg":"庚己合剋甲 甲月份=應期？"},{"pid":"ae30070580b13d224a36f206982a10cf15e162d7","tid":2167162,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fd390a58a61110d77982b8602248d019a6b72a5","tid":216